{"type": "article", "id": 19545, "title": "Nike 和 NFL 的合作花了不少钱，但收益一般", "description": "Nike的核心生意是篮球和跑步，而橄榄球只是很小一部分。", "date": "2015-12-23T06:30:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 3934, "name": "NFL"}, {"id": 4361, "name": "超级碗"}, {"id": 65, "name": "营销"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}], "category": 18, "author": 258307, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134026RoFf4dTzm3qlpgn9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>很多人都知道美国的超级碗，但对 NFL 可能不大熟悉，实际上超级碗就是 NFL（</span><span>美国国家橄榄球联盟）的最后一场比赛。而给这个在美国最受关注的比赛提供</span><span>运动</span><span>装备的就是 Nike，今年是 Nike 和 NFL 合作的第四个年头。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>上周\r\nNike</span><span> </span><span>推出了今年 NFL 新的橄榄球运动服 -Vapor Untouchable，宣称比去年的运动服轻了三分之一。“运动员对新衣服的评价是，‘感觉自己速度更快了。”\r\nNike</span><span> </span><span>橄榄球创意总监 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\">Todd Van Horne</a></span><span> </span><span>说道。不过，粉丝可能不会关心衣服变多轻了，他们更在意为了和球场上的偶像穿一样的衣服，自己得花多少钱</span><span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134026sP58iSXoqcQgIRhb.jpg\" title=\"今年NFL新的运动服\" alt=\"今年NFL新的运动服\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>今年NFL新的运动服</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Nike</span><span> </span><span>在 2012</span><span> </span><span>年与 NFL</span><span> </span><span>签下五年的合约，取代了\r\nAdidas</span><span> </span><span>旗下的 Reebok。根据 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\">Bloomberg</a> 报道，为了能在 NFL</span><span> </span><span>上亮相，Nike</span><span> </span><span>每年得支付 2.2</span><span> </span><span>亿美元，这差不多占到 <span>Nike 每年总营销费用的十分之一</span>，比如 </span>2012 年 Nike 花在广告、运动员代言及赞助上的总费用是 27 亿美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在 Nike 的财务报表上，橄榄球衣服和运动用具都被划分在一个“男士训练”部门，这个部门的发展远远落后于篮球和跑步。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>虽然 </span><span>Nike</span><span> </span><span>拒绝透露 NFL</span><span> </span><span>的赞助为他们带来了多少收益，但从目前的情况看，可能并不乐观。<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\">NFL</a></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\"> </a><span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\">运动员协会</a>透露第一年和 Nike的合作中，运动用具的销售额是 1.5</span><span> </span><span>亿美元。自那以后，销售额就一直不见增长。去年“男式训练”部门的总收入上涨了 4.3%，今年只上涨了 2.2%。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Nike</span><span> </span><span>和 NFL</span><span> </span><span>的合作看起来几乎是个赔本的生意，全球调研公司 NPD</span><span> 副总裁 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\">Matt </a>Powell 预估。不过对 Nike 来说，这可能并不是一个坏的策略，毕竟在一个有 2000</span><span> </span><span>万观众收看的比赛中，每个运动员身上都有 Nike</span><span> </span><span>的标志，这种机会并不太多。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来自 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-18/nike-s-football-business-is-about-adults-buying-expensive-jerseys\">Bloomberg</a><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}